data.description: Do not miss this amazing opportunity.The seller has lowered the price considerably because he needs to move quickly and also OFFER HELP TOWARDS CLOSING COST. Welcome home to maintenance free living and no repairs needed. This beautiful townhouse less than 4 years old offers you an open floor plan and light, bright and neutral colors just waiting for your special touch. The spacious living room with half bath is adjacent to the dining room and kitchen, which features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The dining area has sliding doors that lead to your private screen balcony. Heading upstairs you will find the loft area perfect for an office space and your convenient laundry room upstairs. To the left you will find your spacious master bedroom and bathroom with a large walk-in closet. To the right you will find the other two bedrooms and the bathroom. The stairs and second floor have been recently updated with luxury laminate flooring. The HOA fees include community pool access and maintenance, basic cable, Internet, lawn service and exterior maintenance, pets control and water of irrigation system. The house is located just a couple minutes from Highway 301, a few minutes from I75 near many schools, banks, shops and restaurants.
